title: Age of Empires
description:
The minimum system requirements to run Age of Empires are:

A multimedia PC with a Pentium 90 or faster processor.

Microsoft Windows 95 operating system or later, or Windows NT Workstation 4.0 with Service Pack 3 or later.

16 megabytes (MB) of random access memory (RAM) for Windows 95, or 24 MB of RAM for Windows NT (or for an 8-player multiplayer game in Windows 95/98).

80 MB of available hard disk space.

50 MB of available disk space for swap file.

A local Bus SVGA video adapter with 1 MB of Video RAM and a color SVGA monitor.

A keyboard and Microsoft Mouse or compatible pointing device.

A double-speed (2X) or faster CD-ROM drive for gameplay, or a quad-speed CD-ROM drive for cinematics.

A Windows-compatible sound card with speakers or headphones to hear sound playback.

A 28.8 kilobytes per second (KBPS) or faster modem for head-to-head or Internet play.
